Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:43.80,generic sign style,,0,0,90,,A Day of Colds, Promises and Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:09.60,generic sign style,,0,0,90,,Hunger is the world's best seasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:09.60,generic sign style,,0,0,90,,If we wait just a little longer, it'll taste so much more deliicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:18.05,generic sign style,,0,0,90,,Time, turn back! The food has passed its expiration date!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Kyou-chan, you're already a big sister, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,I'm your big sister! Do you understand me?{I wonder if she understands...}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,She can definitely hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.57,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,derp,Back then, mom was still alive, and dad was kind. Back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Say, Kyou-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,I have a favor to ask of you.{long}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.40,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Back then, I made a promise to mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,A very important promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan! Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I wonder if your fever is gone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,My temperature is the same as yours, so that means it's gone!{FORESHADOWING}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm going to go deliver the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan, don't go out there.{you can't}
Comment: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Because you went on your newspaper run during rainy days, your cold got even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Don't worry! It's all about mind over matter!{病は気から 【やまいはきから】 (exp) sickness and health start with the mind}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan, you should really stay in bed!{blarg}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Our father disappeared after accumulating gambling debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Thus, we were abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan, the rice porridge is done!{粥 【かゆ】 (n) thin rice porridge; watery cooked rice; rice gruel;}
Comment: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Thanks, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's still hot, so be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It really is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You've still got an appetite so I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu, aren't you going to eat?{direct address before or after OH THE HUMANITY}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm not hungry yet.{I don't feel like eating now...}{OMG MOAR FORESHADOWING}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You've been sweating, so I'll have to wash you down and dry you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's hot.{THIS SCENE IS HOT UNF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Is that okay? Do you need more ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,No, it's fine, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,As long as you get lots of rest, I'm sure you'll get better in no time.{I know that I'll feel a whole lot better if we can just curbe that temperature of yours a little.}{Just rest up while I take your temperature periodically and you'll be fine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.90,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,It's kind of nice to catch a cold every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.22,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,No, no! I have to hurry up and get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:22.14,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,I can't continue making Asu worry like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes! I've made a complete recovery.{全快 【ぜんかい】 (n,vs) complete recovery of health}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Well, you had me worried! I'm glad you're better.{good, good}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's all thanks to my little sister's care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It's good to be back at work.{
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I finally beat that cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,For Asu's sake, I have to work extra hard and make up for all the time I took off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Huh? She's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'm home! Asu?
