Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Mr. Landlord! Asu...We have to get Asu to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,What's wrong, Asu? Are you cold?
