Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.25,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,How could I not have noticed?{How come I didn't notice at all?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu had also come down with a cold.{idk too m?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But she still took care of me... Until she collapsed.
