Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,She'll have to stay here as a patient for a while.{I hope you have health care.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I understand. Please take care of her.
