Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Don't tell me you're planning on singing in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Well, that was the idea, but it seems like maybe it wasn't such a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This is a hospital, you know! They'll throw us out!{CREATIVE FUCKING LIBERTIES OKAY}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But I'd love to hear Ichinokura-san's song.{idk anymore. bleh}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Somehow, I feel like it'd help me get better.{fuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Well then, I'll sing because you said so, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.26,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan is late, huh?{on another note, WHY DOESN'T THIS GUY LEARN A NEW FUCKING SONG OH WELL AT LEAST THAT SAVES ME THE AGONY OF FIXING THE HORRIBLY TRANSLATED LYRICS OF AN ALL NEW MASTERPIECE}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,These are Mom's favorite flowers!{hm, rather than sepia, maybe I should add some kind of bloom or something}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,I'll take some to Mom in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Mom always smiles when she sees dandelions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,That's why, if I bring them to her, she'll get better again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:57.33,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Back then, I would gather flowers day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Mom! Mom! I brought you some more flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,There was nothing I could do.{probably could be better linked to the current situation}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Kyou, you brought me some dandelions again, didn't you?{DANDELIONS IN A VASE, YOU SEE FLOWERS IN THESE WEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEDS}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,There's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Even though I promised, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Thank you.{k so would it be weird to make her mom's speech all bloom-y >__>}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Looking at the dandelions you've brought me always helps me forget about my sickness.{FUCK. FUCK. FUCK.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Mom's smile... She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Hey, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Why do you smile whenever you see dandelions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,You see, it's because the dandelions look so happy and carefree to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,They look happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,That's why they remind me of you, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Just like the dandelions, you always seem to be smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,That's why I smile whenever I see dandelions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,That's right. Mom wasn't smiling because she was looking at the dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,She was looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,She was smiling because she saw my smile.{"face" is a more accurate translation but I really like this phrasing better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Even so, I never smiled for Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:09.72,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,For Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.53,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:16.29,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan, don’t try to take anybody else’s place.{lifted right out of episode 4, 17:54}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.58,0:17:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu.{I'm like 90% sure they just forgot to animate her mouth. I think that explains why it magically disappeared.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:24.33,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,You’re my older sister. Stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:29.00,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Okay, I will. I'll be right here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.64,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:37.23,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,I... What the heck was I doing? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,The thing that only I can do for Asu. The most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I wonder if Onee-chan is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I hope she hasn't tired herself out worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,We'll have to handle the hospital fees, too. Maybe I'm just being an annoyance to her.{for fuck's sake could these people be any more self-deprecating}
Comment: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.65,generic sign style,,0,0,90,,Good night, Asu! Get well soon!{jesus fuck she's probably paying more for the batteries them niggerlights is using than the hospital bill will cost.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,O-Onee-chanQ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:53.98,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:55.87,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan's smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It looks just like a dandelion!{okay, I lost it. I just... }
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Congratulations on being discharged, Asu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Make sure to take it easy for a while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Thank you for all you've done.{WHY DO YOU NEED TO THANK THEM, YOU'RE FUCKING PAYING THEM FOR IT :V}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Hey, Onee-chan, there's a place I'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Hey, don't push yourself too much, okay?{tough it out like that anymore}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But, at first, your cold was far worse than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I was so worried about you that I forgot to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Right here, Mom asked me to do something.
Comment: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,It was a long time ago, but this is where I heard it.{um wait...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,I'm your big sister! Do you understand me?{JESUS CHRIST HOW MANY TIMES WILL THEY REPEAT THIS}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Along with Mom's voice.{these are fragments. DO I LOOK LIKE I GIVE A FUCK}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,I ask you, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,90,derp,Protect... Your big sister.{idk this is probably supposed to be broken english anyway but fuck that shitniggersidon'tgiveafucksofuckthatshityoufuckingfaggots}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Your big sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please protect her, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But, Asu, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,No, I don't remember this{her} at all, but I get the feeling that that was what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,That's why I've promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Yes! I'll protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,I will protect Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.54,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,Mother, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:57.42,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,We're keeping our promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.55,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Wow! Onee-chan, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Wow, they're in full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.72,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,90,,We're very happy together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,Onee-chan, this is bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,The sakura-viewing has come inside!{has come to us}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,90,,